Melt butter in large saucepan on medium heat. Add onions; cook 10 min. or until golden brown, stirring frequently. Add broth, 2 soup cans water and steak sauce. Bring to boil. Reduce heat to medium-low; simmer 5 min. Preheat broiler. Ladle soup evenly into 4 large ovenproof bowls. Top with croutons and cheese. Broil 2 to 3 min. or until cheese is melted.